Question: Are both the pots that are to the left of the chef and the pots to the left of the container made of stainless steel?

Reference Answer: Yes, both the pots and the pots are made of stainless steel.

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/2362838.jpg

Program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='chef')
IMAGE0=CROP_LEFTOF(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='pots')
IMAGE1=CROP(image=IMAGE0,box=BOX1)
BOX2=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='container')
IMAGE2=CROP_LEFTOF(image=IMAGE,box=BOX2)
BOX3=LOC(image=IMAGE2,object='pots')
IMAGE3=CROP(image=IMAGE2,box=BOX3)
ANSWER0=VQA(image=IMAGE1,question='What material are the pots made of?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=IMAGE3,question='What material are the pots made of?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER0} == 'stainless steel' and {ANSWER1} == 'stainless steel' else 'no'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
